[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "SIR THOMAS BROWNE",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Looking back to those days of old, ere the gate shut behind me, I can see now that to children with a proper equipment of parents these things would have worn a different aspect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "These elders, our betters by a trick of chance, commanded no respect, but only a certain blend of envy-of their good luck-and pity-for their inability to make use of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "For them the orchard (a place elf haunted, wonderful!) simply produced so many apples and cherries: or it didn't, when the failures of Nature were not infrequently ascribed to us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Perhaps, indeed, it was one of their best qualities that they spent the greater part of their time stuffily indoors.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "To be sure, there was an exception in the curate, who would receive unblenching the information that the meadow beyond the orchard was a prairie studded with herds of buffalo, which it was our delight, moccasined and tomahawked, to ride down with those whoops that announce the scenting of blood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Then brute force was pitilessly applied.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000013_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000013_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "But was the matter allowed to end there? I trow not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "The Olympians are all past and gone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142396_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142396/1737_142396_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "A saddening doubt, a dull suspicion, creeps over me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "She panted up anon, and dropped on the turf beside me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "\"Where's Harold;\" I asked presently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "\"Come on and let's be surprised.\" But I could not help feeling that on this day of days even a grizzly felt misplaced and common.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "\"Why, there aren't any good lions,\" said Harold, hastily.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "\"Oh yes, there are, heaps and heaps,\" contradicted Edward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Earth to earth!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000027_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000027_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Humanity would have rejected it with scorn, Nature, everywhere singing in the same key, recognised and accepted it without a flicker of dissent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "\"Take me for guide to day,\" he seemed to plead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "To day why not I, the trickster, the hypocrite?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000028_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000028_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "So we sheered off together, arm in arm, so to speak; and with fullest confidence I took the jigging, thwartwise course my chainless pilot laid for me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "As a rule this sort of thing struck me as the most pitiful tomfoolery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "From forth the vestry window projected two small legs, gyrating, hungry for foothold, with larceny-not to say sacrilege-in their every wriggle: a godless sight for a supporter of the Establishment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Bill's coveted booty, too, I could easily guess at that; it came from the Vicar's store of biscuits, kept (as I knew) in a cupboard along with his official trappings.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Nature, who had accepted me for ally, cared little who had the world's biscuits, and assuredly was not going to let any friend of hers waste his time in playing policeman for Society.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Like a black pirate flag on the blue ocean of air, a hawk hung ominous; then, plummet wise, dropped to the hedgerow, whence there rose, thin and shrill, a piteous voice of squealing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Further on, a hedgehog lay dead athwart the path-nay, more than dead; decadent, distinctly; a sorry sight for one that had known the fellow in more bustling circumstances.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_142397_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/142397/1737_142397_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Harold, it further appeared, greatly coveting tadpoles, and top heavy with the eagerness of possession, had fallen into the pond. This, in itself, was nothing; but on attempting to sneak in by the back door, he had rendered up his duckweed bedabbled person into the hands of an aunt, and had been promptly sent off to bed; and this, on a holiday, was very much.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "This may either be done in Shetland or German wool, and is very pretty in black Shetland wool.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Cast on three stitches; increase at the beginning of each row till you have twelve.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "First pattern row:--Make one, knit two together, knit three, make one, knit one, make one, knit three, knit two together, knit one, make one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Second row:--Seamed, making a stitch at the beginning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Third row:--Make one, knit one, knit two together, knit two, make one, knit three, make one, knit two, knit two together, knit two.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Fifth row:--Make one, knit two, knit two together, knit one, make one, knit five, make one, knit one, knit two together, knit three.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Sixth row:--Seamed, making one at the beginning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Seventh row:--Make one, knit three, knit two together, make one, knit seven, make one, knit two together, knit four.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1737/146161/1737_146161_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1737",
        "content": "Ninth row:--Make one, knit five, make one, knit three, knit two together, knit four, make one, and knit the remainder.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1737_146161_000010_000000",
